Comment: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.02,Default,tc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}夢想的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.51,0:24:56.01,Default,sc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}扩张的意识
Comment: 0,0:24:52.51,0:24:56.01,Default,tc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}擴張的意識
